{% comment %}
  Hemlock & Oak Product Finder — Shopify Page Template

  SETUP:
  1. Upload this file to your theme's templates/ folder as "page.product-finder.liquid"
     OR paste the HTML below into a custom page's content (Shopify Admin > Pages)
  2. Upload finder.css and finder.js to theme Assets/

  Product data is fetched live from Shopify's built-in AJAX API (/products.json).
  No API tokens, no sync, no Liquid data output needed — always current.
  finder.js detects it's on Shopify and fetches automatically.
{% endcomment %}

{{ 'finder.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<div class="finder-container" id="finder-app">
  <div style="text-align:center; padding:60px 20px; color:#6B6B6B;">
    Loading product finder&hellip;
  </div>
</div>

<script src="{{ 'finder.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
